reviewText: Great drama of finding love and hope when least expected!

I am waiting to watch it with my roommates but I'm hoping that it's good it sounds interesting I have not seen this before and they made me promise to wait until after winter break to watch it with them

This is one of those dramas that will have you say what the...and in the next breath say you go girl. The heroine is a strong character who has her moment when she wavers her devotion to her older brother the typical mother you want to hate and just be amazed that the heroine is as normal as she is with her family. Over all it's a good drama.
